OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1771879289
OL,3,CDriver who reached speeds of over
OL,4,C100mph jailed for causing death of mum
OL,6,FA driver who reached speeds of up to
OL,7,F114mph has been jailed for causing the
OL,8,Fdeath of a mother on North Tyneside.
OL,10,FRyan Scott, 28, of Chasedale Crescent
OL,11,Fin Blyth, was sentenced to 10 years in
OL,12,Fprison and banned from driving for 13
OL,13,Fyears and eight months.
OL,15,FClaire Laybourne was travelling in a
OL,16,FVolkswagen T-Roc when a Skoda Fabia
OL,17,Fdriven by Scott on the northbound
OL,18,Fcarriageway of the A19 crashed into
OL,19,Fher car, at about 10:40pm on 5
OL,20,FDecember. She died the next day.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/6
