FL,423,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1771879289
OL,3,CDriver who reached speeds of over
OL,4,C100mph jailed for causing death of mum
OL,6,FScott had previously admitted causing
OL,7,Fdeath by dangerous driving, causing
OL,8,Fserious injury to another female by
OL,9,Fdangerous driving and causing death by
OL,10,Fdriving while uninsured.
OL,12,FIn victim impact statements heard at
OL,13,FNewcastle Crown Court on Monday (23
OL,14,FFebruary), Ms Laybourne's fiance and
OL,15,Fpartner, Ben, of 14 years described
OL,16,Fher as "kind, caring, funny and full
OL,17,Fof warmth".
OL,19,FHe added: "There is not a minute that
OL,20,Fpasses where I do not feel her absence
OL,21,Fin every room.
OL,26,@{D@KOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/6
