OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,423,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1771879289
OL,3,CDriver who reached speeds of over
OL,4,C100mph jailed for causing death of mum
OL,6,F"Waking up every morning without her
OL,7,Frestarts the heartbreak. Returning to
OL,8,Fan empty house and the lonely nights
OL,9,Fwhere we would normally be discussing
OL,10,Fboring everyday things, break me all
OL,11,Fover again.
OL,13,F"Claire was deeply loved by everyone
OL,14,Fshe met. She truly touched so many
OL,15,Fpeople."
OL,17,FFollowing the crash, police said Scott
OL,18,Ffled the scene on foot.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
