OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1771879289
OL,3,CDriver who reached speeds of over
OL,4,C100mph jailed for causing death of mum
OL,6,FA saliva DNA sample taken from the
OL,7,FSkoda's air bag matched perfectly with
OL,8,FScott's ` placing only him behind the
OL,9,Fwheel at the time of the collision.
OL,11,FFurther data taken from the vehicle
OL,12,Fshowed Scott travelling at a speed of
OL,13,F112mph just five seconds before the
OL,14,Fcollision.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
