OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,423,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1771879289
OL,3,CDriver who reached speeds of over
OL,4,C100mph jailed for causing death of mum
OL,6,FWith a potential collision up ahead
OL,7,Fand Scott failing to brake, the car's
OL,8,Fanti-lock braking system took over
OL,9,Fslowing the vehicle down to just under
OL,10,F90mph at the time of the collision `
OL,11,Fstill almost 20mph in excess of the
OL,12,Froad's speed limit, police said.
OL,14,FLeading on the investigation was
OL,15,FSergeant Dave Roberts, of the Force's
OL,16,FSerious Collision Investigation Unit,
OL,17,Fhe said: "While we welcome the jail
OL,18,Ftime Scott has been served, no
OL,19,Fsentence will ever make up for his
OL,20,Freprehensible actions on that day.
OL,26,@yD@JOU
