CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1771879289
OL,3,CDriver who reached speeds of over
OL,4,C100mph jailed for causing death of mum
OL,6,F"Our thoughts remain firmly with
OL,7,FClaire's family as they begin to
OL,8,Fnavigate a life without their partner,
OL,9,Fmother, daughter, auntie and loyal
OL,10,Ffriend.
OL,12,F"Claire was simply travelling home `
OL,13,Fshe should not have ended up losing
OL,14,Fher life that evening.
OL,16,F"Scott's decision to take to the wheel
OL,17,Fin an incredibly dangerous manner saw
OL,18,Fone woman lose her life and left her
OL,19,Ffamily's lives shattered."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUxD@AOU{D@ZO]
